{
  "chapter": 81,
  "chapter_summary": "第八十一回\"生死两难\"。花无缺身中销魂针，笑穴被制，真气虽通却无法停止狂笑。江玉郎趁机以暗器攻击，花无缺施展移花接玉将其击退，逼其放走铁心兰后江玉郎逃遁。花无缺狂笑不止，内心痛苦万分，为不让铁心兰看到自己惨死的真相，故意以恶言将她赶走。铁心兰去而复返，识破花无缺伪装，死活不肯离去，两人在山林中生离死别。花无缺为让铁心兰死心，毅然离去。他独返山君神庙，击倒猛虎，毁坏庄院，呼喊白山君决战却无人应答。花无缺力竭倒在椅上，白夫人出现，领他观看白山君的尸首——她已亲手杀了丈夫。白夫人忏悔二十年来的过错，告知花无缺笑穴中的销魂针已深入难取，但世上有人能救他，她可延长其三日性命带他前往求医。花无缺终于被说动，同意前往。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好，你既然要死，我就索性成全了你吧！杀个把人，想来也不会妨碍我享受的兴致的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你疯了么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你……你敢！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好一着移花接玉！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你方才难道是在装模作样？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "不错……哈哈……还不放下她来！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我……我放下她，你就放了我？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "放……放……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你将我们都骗过了，害我们为你着急，你觉得很好笑么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你觉得这玩笑开得很好笑么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你可以不笑了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你……你再要这样笑下去，我就走了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你走吧！哈哈……我反正已知道你爱的不是我……哈哈哈，你快走吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你真要我走？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好．我走就走，我……我现在才知道你是这样的人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你又回来做什么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "告诉我，这究竟是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "什么事？……哈哈，我只是觉得你好笑。哈哈哈，你难道连赶都赶不走？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我知道你绝不是这样的人，我不能走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你不走？哈哈，好，我走！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "告诉我，你……你是不是受了种很奇怪的伤？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我怎会受伤？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你为何不肯说实话？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我知道你是为了我，才变成这样子的，你……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我为了你……哈哈，你还是快去找江小鱼，快去快去！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我不去，我谁也不找，我一定要陪着你，无论谁也不能要我走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "江小鱼呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "小鱼儿？……我早已忘记他了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "但你还是忘不了他的，哈哈……爱，并不是交换，哈哈哈，你若爱一个人，无论他怎样对你，你都是爱他的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你还是去找他吧……好生照顾他，知道么……哈哈……但望你们一辈子过得快快活活……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花无缺，你这混帐……你若这样死了，我能嫁给小鱼儿么？你若这样死了，我们这一生，又怎么会再有一天快活？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花无缺，花无缺……你回来吧！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花无缺呀花无缺，你至少现在还是活着的，你至少还可以用这短促的生命做一番事业。你就算要死，也不该死得无声无息。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "白山君，你出来吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "白山君，你听着，我虽然要死了，但我也要将你们这些阴毒的人全都杀死，为世人除害！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "白山君！白山君！你在哪里！你为何不肯出来与我一战？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "你来得正好，既来了为何还不出手？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "原来你只是来看着我死的么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "很好，无论你为何而来，我都很感激你，我正在觉得寂寞。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "可怜的人，你竟连求生的勇气都没有了么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "你一心只求我速死，却反来要我求生，你难道还觉得我的痛苦不够？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "但我也知道我是对不起你的，只求你能原谅我。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "你为什么要说这些话？难道又想来骗我么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我也知道你是绝不会相信我的，但……但你能跟我去瞧一样东西么？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我只求你这一次，无论如何，这对你也不会再有什么伤害是么？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "不错，我既已将死，还有什么人能伤害我？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "白山君死了！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我要你亲眼瞧见他的尸身，也正是因为我觉得对不起你……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "你杀了他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "不错，是我杀了他。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我那么样对你，只因我一心还在想挽回他的心，我为了他，不惜伤害任何人，不惜做出任何事……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "但你既然如此对他，为何又杀了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "他竟丝毫不念夫妻之情，他……他……他竟要杀我！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "所以……你就杀了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我本来虽然不惜为他而死的，但他真要来杀我时，我却再也忍受不住。二十年来所受的折磨和委屈，二十年来的冤苦和悲痛，全都在这一瞬间发作出来，我忍不住抽出了刀，一刀向他刺了过去。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我本也以为这一刀大概伤不了他，谁知他从未想到我会反抗，竟毫无防备之心，我这一刀，竟真的……真的将他刺死了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "过去的事，不必再提，我……我绝不会再恨你……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你原谅了我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "你话已说完了么？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我该说的都已说了，你……你难道没有话要对我说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "我……我只望你……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "其实用不着你说，我也早该为你起出笑穴中那根销魂针的。但你方才用力过度，针已入穴极深，我也无力为你起出来了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你现在还不能走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "事已至此，你为何还要留下我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "世上还有个能救你的人，我虽然无力救你，但却能将你的性命延长三天，三天内，我就可以带你去找到那个人，你若想活下去，你就该有勇气去求他。你年纪轻轻，求人并不可耻，不敢活下去才真正可耻。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "我纵去求他，他也未必会救我，我又何苦……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我很了解那个人，只要你去，他一定会救你的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "何况，你并不是去求他，你只不过去治病而已。一个人生了病而不去就医，这人并不可敬，反而可笑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    }
